  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate how measures of frailty, assessed during occupational therapy (OT) evaluation&#xD;
      and intervention impact decision for advanced heart failure (HF) therapies and postoperative&#xD;
      outcomes.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
